metadata.name: Yellow Streak
metadata.description:
In the busy streets of cities, people are always in a hurry.
They are rushing to catch the next train, hurrying to their next meeting or appointment, or simply trying to keep up with the fast-paced world around them.
There is a constant sense of urgency, whether it's due to pressure to be productive or the need to be efficient with time.
This fast-paced lifestyle can be both exciting and tiring, as individuals strive to keep up with the never-ending demands of life.


Shot in Belgium
Sony A7RV - 90mm - F22 - ISO50 - 1s
5946X8919
